==English==

===Etymology===
From [[explore]] + [[pornography]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# A [[fascination]] with [[historic]] [[exploration]]s; either [[reading]] about them or [[watching]] [[television]] [[programme]]s (''[[softcore]]'') or physically [[reenacting]] them (''[[hardcore]]'')

